from Crypto.Util.number import *
def print_scheme():
    ct = [{i: 0 for i in range(5)} for _ in range(32)]
    keys = 5
    offset = 0
    for _ in range(5):
        for i in range(32):
            ct[i][offset] = (1 + ct[i][offset])%2
            for j in range(keys):
                if i & 2**j: ct[i][j+offset] = (1 + ct[i][j+offset])%2
        keys -= 1
        offset += 1
    for i in range(len(ct)):
        s = f'ct{i} = pt{i}'
        for j in ct[i].keys():
            if ct[i][j]: s += f' ^ k{j}'
        ct[i] = s
    ct = '\n'.join(ct)
    print(ct)
